The paper discusses the use of altmetrics, which are primarily used in the fields of digital libraries (cs.DL), social media (cs.SOC), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CYBER), and possibly also in social informatics (cs.SI). The focus on bibliometrics also suggests a potential fit with cs.DL and cs.IR.
